"     Peter J Barnes, DM, DSc, FRCP, FRS",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials contributorType\" href=\"UTD.htm?16/46/17130/contributors\">",
"     Section Editor",
